{"tid":1162509,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"For驚中招又唔想露面嘅人做嘅檢查","createTime":"2019-05-20T02:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T02:17:15.000Z","uid":227804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1b315779211ea8768730e6ff83ea8bb75d44e137","tid":1162509,"uid":227804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:13:15.000Z","msg":"[免費, 免露面]快遞檢測 &ndash;  愛滋病病毒、淋病及衣原體 (名額有限)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NG2Z1Ei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNG2Z1Ei.jpg&h=a1f1b8bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時夾不到時間去診所／非牟利機構做愛滋病和性病檢查？<br />\n怕尷尬，不想去面對職員？或者你可以試試「自我檢測」，測試過程及測試結果都是自己在私密的環境進行；拿取測試工具及遞交樣本都只須到順豐站，而且費用全免！<br />\n<br />\n申請流程：填問卷-&gt;開帳號-&gt;選最近的順豐站-&gt;等職員電話確認-&gt;順豐站拿取測試工具-&gt;自己檢測-&gt;到順豐站交樣本-&gt;2星期後網上查閱結果。<br />\n<br />\n_________________________________________________________<br />\n＊本計劃由再思社區健康組織(C.H.O.I.C.E.)、香港中文大學及衞生署社會衞生科合辦。<br />\n<br />\n參加者須合乎以下資格: <br />\n1. 25歲或以下，懂中文 <br />\n2. 短期於2個月內不會離開香港 <br />\n3. 研究全屬自願性質<br />\n___________________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n參加方法<br />\n<br />\n1. 進入網站：【<a href=\"https://www.echaticheck.com/】\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.echaticheck.com%2F%E3%80%91&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ154O1D3QR3Td9ugMDSJ%2BOB4%3D&h=302b815e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.echaticheck.com/】</a> <br />\n2. 點擊【匿名風險評估】<br />\n3. 細閱流程後，點擊【進行問卷調查】，完成問卷（需時約5-10分鐘）<br />\n4. 再進入網站：【<a href=\"https://www.echaticheck.com/】，點擊【選取測試套裝】\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.echaticheck.com%2F%E3%80%91%EF%BC%8C%E9%BB%9E%E6%93%8A%E3%80%90%E9%81%B8%E5%8F%96%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E5%A5%97%E8%A3%9D%E3%80%91&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ154O1D3QR3Td9ugMDSJ%2BOB4%3D&h=866a9fac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.echaticheck.com/】，點擊【選取測試套裝】</a><br />\n5. 點擊【Sign Up】，填寫Email電郵及Password密碼<br />\n6. 【揀選順豐站地址】並填寫資料<br />\n7. C.H.O.I.C.E職員會於5個工作天內主動聯絡你<br />\n8. 數天後將會收到順豐快遞取件訊息，請必須於3天內取件<br />\n9. 請按照測試套裝附上的說明書抽取樣本。樣本必須於3天內要透過順豐快遞寄回中文大學。<br />\n10. 樣本寄出後約兩星期，再登入網站【<a href=\"https://www.echaticheck.com/】，點擊【查閱測試結果】，輸入已註冊的電郵及密碼，查閱檢測結果。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.echaticheck.com%2F%E3%80%91%EF%BC%8C%E9%BB%9E%E6%93%8A%E3%80%90%E6%9F%A5%E9%96%B1%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C%E3%80%91%EF%BC%8C%E8%BC%B8%E5%85%A5%E5%B7%B2%E8%A8%BB%E5%86%8A%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%BB%E9%83%B5%E5%8F%8A%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC%EF%BC%8C%E6%9F%A5%E9%96%B1%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C%E3%80%82&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ154O1D3QR3Td9ugMDSJ%2BOB4%3D&h=92aba224\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.echaticheck.com/】，點擊【查閱測試結果】，輸入已註冊的電郵及密碼，查閱檢測結果。</a>                                                                                                                                                                                                               <br />\n<br />\n如遇上任何問題，請致電66416006聯絡我們。"},{"pid":"9fd1bcbcdfa8c96ab48547e853bb3f4ade920aad","tid":1162509,"uid":187198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:12:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc4acc57f797b339b6b776669922c47f8f9a9d6","tid":1162509,"uid":87313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:17:15.000Z","msg":"屌屌屌"}]}